<div class="gs-group-messages-privacy" title="Privacy"
     tal:attributes="title string:Post visibility: ${options/visibility}">
  <ul>
    <li>
      <span class="grouping" 
            tal:content="structure options/webVisibility">Party people</span> 
      will be able to see your post on the web, and
      <span class="grouping" 
            tal:content="structure options/emailVisibility">party people</span>
    will receive an email from you.</li>
    <li>
      Your post on the <strong>web</strong> will contain your 
      message, and link to your profile. 
    Your email address will be hidden.</li>
    <li>
      The <strong>email</strong> will contain your message, your
    email address, and a link to your post on the web.</li>
  </ul>
</div><!--gs-group-messages-privacy-->
